T02TD3011E:64b-0: @64b * // dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3011E:64b-1: dbang po nyams pa gso bar byed pa'i las kyi bye brag ni /
T02TD3011E:64b-2: dang po mig gi nad las grol bar 'dod pa'i sgrub pa po dam tshig dang ldan pas /
T02TD3011E:64b-3: khrus kyi cho gnas ji ltar 'byung ba'i khrus byas te /
T02TD3011E:64b-4: gos gsar pa gyon pa dang smyung bar gnas pa la sogs pa byas nas khrus lan brgya rtsa brgyad byas te /
T02TD3011E:64b-5: de nas bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du byas la /
T02TD3011E:64b-6: bdag nyid kyi snying ga'i sa bon las gzungs gyi lha dpag tu med pa sgros te /
T02TD3011E:64b-7: 'phags pa mchod la sems can gyi don bya pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ma lus par byas nas bdag gi mig la thim pas /
T02TD3011E:64b-8: sangs rgyas kyi spyan dri ma med pa thob cing yongs su dag par mkhyen pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par dmigs shing /
T02TD3011E:64b-9: autpal sngon po dang skyer khanda la snying po rgyas bsdus kyi sngags ci rigs par bzlas shing byug go //
T02TD3011E:64b-10: tshag pa la ni spangs ma la bzlas shing byug go //
T02TD3011E:64b-11: rab rib can rnams la ni aa ru ra'i khu ba la bsngags te byug go //
T02TD3011E:64b-12: ling thog can rnams la mtshal dang cong zhi'i khu ba la bsngags la byug go //
T02TD3011E:64b-13: sha mdzor dang zug cheb rnams la ka ra dang mi'i 'o ma la bzlas la byug go //
T02TD3011E:64b-14: de ltar byas pas gdon dang nad gang yin pa yang zhi bar nges so //
T02TD3011E:64b-15: mig gi dbang po nyams pa gso ba'i cho ga gsal ba'i snang ba zhes bya ba /
T02TD3011E:65a-0: slob dpon ye shes rdo rjes @65a * //
